==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|entretenir|lang=fro}}, from {{term|entre||among|lang=fro}} + {{term|tenir||to hold|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|inter|lang=la}} + {{term|teneo|teneō|hold, keep|lang=la}}. For the noun, compare French {{term|entretien|lang=fr}}.

